cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CE, cs.CY, cs.DB

The paper discusses the use of machine learning and artificial intelligence in healthcare, specifically in the treatment of sepsis patients. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of data sets and databases (cs.DB) to train the AI Clinician. Additionally, the paper discusses the optimization of treatment strategies (cs.CE) and the potential ethical considerations (cs.CY) involved in using AI in healthcare.
